org.hps.conditions.svt

Class SvtConditions

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.conditions.svt.AbstractSvtConditions
      • org.hps.conditions.svt.SvtConditions

  • public final class SvtConditions
extends AbstractSvtConditions
    This class contains all test run SVT conditions data by readout channel. SvtChannel objects from the SVT channel map can be used to lookup the conditions for individual channels.
